trans-unit.source: Provides a way for developers to declare static connections in a content page when a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager"></xref> control has been declared in the content page's associated master page.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en metode for utviklere å deklarere statisk tilkoblinger i en innhold siden når en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager"> </xref> kontrollen er deklarert i innhold siden tilknyttede hoveddokumentet.

trans-unit.source: The ProxyWebPartManager control exists for the particular scenario of declaring static connections in content pages when a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control has already been declared in a master page.
trans-unit.target: ProxyWebPartManager kontrollen finnes for et bestemt scenario av deklarerer statisk tilkoblinger i innhold sider når en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontrollen er allerede deklarert i en hoveddokumentet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: By design, a Web page that uses Web Parts controls must contain one (and only one) <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control that manages all Web Parts controls on the page.
trans-unit.target: Som standard en nettside som bruker webdeler kontroller må inneholde ett (og bare én) <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontroll som administrerer alle webdeler vises på siden.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: When a Web Parts application uses master pages, it is common to place the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control in the master page, because all the content pages are merged with the master page at run time and the single <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control will manage all the Web Parts controls from all content pages.
trans-unit.target: Når en webdeler-programmet bruker master sider, er det vanlige skal plasseres i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontrollerer i hoveddokumentet, fordi alle innhold sider som skal slås sammen med hoveddokumentet ved kjøring og enkelt <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontrollen skal administrere alle webdeler kontroller fra alle innhold sidene.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: However, when developers want to declare static connections in the content pages of such an application, they might seem to face a limitation.
trans-unit.target: Når utviklere vil deklarere statisk tilkoblinger i innhold sidene i et slikt program, kan de kan virke å møte en begrensning.

trans-unit.source: A static Web Parts connection can be declared only by adding an <`asp:webpartconnection>` element as a child of a `<staticconnections>` element, which itself must be a child of a `<asp:webpartmanager>` element.
trans-unit.target: En statisk webdeler tilkobling kan deklareres bare ved å legge til en `asp:webpartconnection>` elementet som en underordnet av en `<staticconnections>` elementet som selve må være en underordnet av en `<asp:webpartmanager>` elementet.

trans-unit.source: But because the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control was already declared in the master page, and is the one permitted <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control, developers cannot declare additional <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> controls in the content pages to add static connections.
trans-unit.target: Men fordi den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontrollen var allerede deklarert i hoveddokumentet, og tillates i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontroll, utviklere kan ikke deklarere mer <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>Kontroller i igjen å legge til statisk tilkoblinger.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: The ProxyWebPartManager control takes the place of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control in this scenario.
trans-unit.target: Kontrollen ProxyWebPartManager står i stedet for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontrollen i dette scenarioet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: Developers declare an `<asp:proxywebpartmanager>` element instead of an `<asp:webpartmanager>` element in their content pages, and can then declare static connections as child elements.
trans-unit.target: Utviklere deklarere en `<asp:proxywebpartmanager>` elementet i stedet for en `<asp:webpartmanager>` elementet i innhold sider, og kan deretter deklarere statisk tilkoblinger som underordnede elementer.

trans-unit.source: At run time, the connections in the ProxyWebPartManager control are simply added to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A> collection of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control and treated like any other connection.
trans-unit.target: Kjøretid tilkoblinger i kontrollen ProxyWebPartManager ganske enkelt legges til i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A>samling av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontrollere og behandles som en annen tilkobling.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A>

trans-unit.source: Because the ProxyWebPartManager control is used only in this particular development scenario, it has more limited functionality than the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> class.
trans-unit.target: ProxyWebPartManager kontrollen brukes bare i dette tilfellet for bestemte development, er det mer begrenset funksjonalitet enn <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>klasse.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: In fact, although the ProxyWebPartManager control acts as a proxy to contain static connections for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control in content pages, it does not inherit from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control.
trans-unit.target: Faktisk selv om kontrollen ProxyWebPartManager fungerer som proxy skal inneholde statisk tilkoblinger for det <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontrollen i innhold sider, den arver ikke fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: It inherits directly from the <xref:System.Web.UI.Control> class, and overrides only a few of the base members.
trans-unit.target: Arver direkte fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.Control>klasse, og overstyrer noen av de grunnleggende medlemmene.</xref:System.Web.UI.Control>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.EnableTheming%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.Visible%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.SkinID%2A> properties are overridden and assigned values that prevent them from being used.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.EnableTheming%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.Visible%2A>, og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.SkinID%2A>egenskaper overstyres og tilordnes verdier som hindrer brukes.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.SkinID%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.Visible%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.EnableTheming%2A>

trans-unit.source: Other inherited properties are overridden to adjust their design-time behavior, but otherwise they have the same behavior as the base properties.
trans-unit.target: Andre arvede egenskaper overstyres for å justere utformingen virkemåten, men hvis de har på samme måte som egenskaper base.

trans-unit.source: These include the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.Controls%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.ClientID%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: Dette inkluderer de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.Controls%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.ClientID%2A>Egenskaper.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.ClientID%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.Controls%2A>

trans-unit.source: Finally, the ProxyWebPartManager class has one non-inherited property.
trans-unit.target: Til slutt har ProxyWebPartManager klassen én arvet egenskap.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A> property returns its own collection of static connections (a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartConnectionCollection> object).
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A>egenskapen returnerer sin egen samling av statiske tilkoblingene (en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartConnectionCollection>objektet).</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartConnectionCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A>

trans-unit.source: As for methods, the ProxyWebPartManager class similarly overrides only a few methods, mostly to restrict their use.
trans-unit.target: Som metoder overstyrer klassen ProxyWebPartManager på samme måte bare noen metoder, vanligvis for å begrense bruk.

trans-unit.source: The inherited <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.Focus%2A> method is made unusable by throwing an exception if called.
trans-unit.target: Arvet <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.Focus%2A>metoden utføres ikke kan brukes av et unntak hvis kalles.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.Focus%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.CreateControlCollection%2A> method always returns an empty control collection, which has the effect of preventing it from being able to contain a collection of controls.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.CreateControlCollection%2A>returneres en tom kontrollsamling som har innvirkning på forhindrer at den kan inneholde en samling av kontroller alltid.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.CreateControlCollection%2A>

trans-unit.source: Finally, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.OnInit%2A> method calls the base method, and then assigns the collection of connections referenced by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A> property to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control.
trans-unit.target: Til slutt den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.OnInit%2A>kaller base-metoden, og tilordner samlingen av tilkoblinger refererer til den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A>egenskapen til den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A?displayProperty=fullName>for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.OnInit%2A>

trans-unit.source: This has the effect of rolling up all the static connections declared in all content pages and making them part of the connections collection maintained by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control in the master page.
trans-unit.target: Dette har innvirkning på fremheve alle statiske tilkoblingene deklarert i alle innhold sider og slik at de er en del av samlingen tilkoblinger vedlikeholdt av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontrollen i hoveddokumentet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.target: Kontroll-IDen for HTML-koden som genereres av ASP.NET.

trans-unit.target: Overstyrer egenskapen basistabellen slik at den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager"> </xref> kontrollen fra med kontroller.

trans-unit.source: The CreateControlCollection method overrides the base method to prevent the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager> control from containing and returning collections of controls.
trans-unit.target: Metoden CreateControlCollection overstyrer metoden basistabellen slik at den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>kontrollen fra som inneholder og returnerer samlinger med kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: Its only purpose is to enable static connections to be declared in content pages within an application that uses master pages.
trans-unit.target: Formålet bare er å aktivere statisk tilkoblinger til deklareres i innhold sider i et program som bruker master sider.

trans-unit.source: Always returns an <xref href="System.Web.UI.EmptyControlCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer alltid en <xref href="System.Web.UI.EmptyControlCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Overrides the base property to prevent themes from being used.
trans-unit.target: Overstyrer egenskapen base for å hindre at oppsett blir brukt.

trans-unit.source: The EnableTheming property overrides the base property to prevent themes from being used with the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager> control.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen EnableTheming overstyrer egenskapen base for å hindre at oppsett brukes med den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: This is to prevent it coming into conflict with any themes being used with the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control in the master page (its <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.EnableTheming%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property always returns `true`).
trans-unit.target: Dette er at den kommer i konflikt med en tema brukes med den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontrollen i hoveddokumentet (den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.EnableTheming%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen returnerer alltid `true`).</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.EnableTheming%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: Always returns <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>, to prevent themes from being used.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer alltid <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>, for å hindre at oppsett blir brukt.

trans-unit.target: En oppringer prøver å tilordne en verdi for denne egenskapen.

trans-unit.source: Overrides the base method to prevent the method from being called.
trans-unit.target: Overstyrer base metode for å hindre at metoden blir kalt.

trans-unit.source: The Focus method overrides the base method and throws an exception if any caller attempts to call the method.
trans-unit.target: Metoden fokus overstyrer metoden base og oppstår det et unntak hvis noen oppkaller forsøker å kalle metoden.

trans-unit.source: This is because the inherited <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.Focus%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method is designed for controls with a user interface (UI), but the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager> control has no UI and therefore has no need to set the focus.
trans-unit.target: Fordi arvet <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.Focus%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metode er utformet for kontroller med brukergrensesnittet (UI), men <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>kontrollen har ingen Brukergrensesnittet og er derfor ingen grunn til å angi fokus.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.Control.Focus%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.target: Hever den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Control.Init"> </xref> hendelsen og initialiserer kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The OnInit method calls the base method, and then carries out tasks to initialize the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager> control.
trans-unit.target: Metoden OnInit kaller base-metoden, og deretter utfører oppgaver initialisere den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: An important task of this method is to assign the collection of connections referenced by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A> property to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control's <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A?displayProperty=fullName> collection.
trans-unit.target: En viktig oppgave av denne metoden er å tilordne samlingen av tilkoblinger refererer til den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A>egenskapen til det <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontrollens <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A?displayProperty=fullName>samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.EventArgs> that contains the event data.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.EventArgs>som inneholder Hendelsesdata.</xref:System.EventArgs>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager"></xref> control from the associated master page is <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager"> </xref> kontrollen fra tilknyttede hoveddokumentet er <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Overrides the base property to prevent a value from being assigned.
trans-unit.target: Overstyrer egenskapen base for å hindre at en verdi ble tilordnet.

trans-unit.source: The SkinID property overrides the base property to prevent a value from being assigned to it, which has the effect of preventing skins from being used with the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager> control.
trans-unit.target: SkinID egenskapen overstyrer base egenskapen for å hindre at en verdi ble tilordnet til den, som har forhindre skallene brukes med den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: This is done because the control never exposes a user interface (UI) on a page.
trans-unit.target: Dette gjøres fordi kontrollen aldri viser brukergrensesnittet (UI) på en side.

trans-unit.source: The same behavior is implemented by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control for its <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.SkinID%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: På samme måte implementeres av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontrollere for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.SkinID%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.SkinID%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: Always returns an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: Returnerer alltid en tom streng ("").

trans-unit.target: En oppringer prøver å tilordne en verdi for denne egenskapen.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of static connections declared within the <xref uid="langword_csharp_<asp:proxywebpartmanager>" name="<asp:proxywebpartmanager>" href=""></xref> element on a content page.
trans-unit.target: Henter en samling av statiske tilkoblinger som er angitt i den <xref uid="langword_csharp_<asp:proxywebpartmanager>" name="<asp:proxywebpartmanager>" href=""> </xref> elementet i et.

trans-unit.source: The StaticConnections property references the collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection> objects declared in an `<asp:proxywebpartmanager>` element.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen StaticConnections refererer til samlingen av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection>objekter som er deklarert i en `<asp:proxywebpartmanager>` element.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection>

trans-unit.source: The connections contained in this collection are added to the static connections of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> controls (referenced by its <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A?displayProperty=fullName> collection), and treated exactly like any other connections associated with the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control.
trans-unit.target: Tilkoblinger i denne samlingen er lagt til i de statiske tilkoblingene for det <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>Kontroller (referert til av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A?displayProperty=fullName>samling), og behandles nøyaktig som andre tilkoblinger som er knyttet til den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: The declarative element that corresponds to the StaticConnections property is the `<staticconnections>` element.
trans-unit.target: Det deklarerende elementet som tilsvarer egenskapen StaticConnections er den `<staticconnections>` elementet.

trans-unit.source: In an application that uses master pages, the `<staticconnections>` element is added as a child of the `<asp:proxywebpartmanager>` element on a content page, and an `<asp:webpartconnection>` element in turn is added as a child of the `<staticconnections>` element.
trans-unit.target: I en applikasjon som bruker master sider i `<staticconnections>` elementet er lagt til som en underordnet av den `<asp:proxywebpartmanager>` elementet i et, og en `<asp:webpartconnection>` elementet i sin tur er lagt til som en underordnet av den `<staticconnections>` elementet.

trans-unit.source: Multiple `<asp:webpartconnection>` elements can be added to one `<staticconnections>` element, and multiple content pages can declare static connections as part of a master pages application.
trans-unit.target: Flere `<asp:webpartconnection>` elementer kan legges til en `<staticconnections>` element og flere innhold sider kan deklarere statisk tilkoblinger som en del av en master pages-program.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartConnectionCollection"></xref> that contains all static <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection"></xref> objects declared within an <xref uid="langword_csharp_<asp:proxywebpartmanager>" name="<asp:proxywebpartmanager>" href=""></xref> element.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartConnectionCollection"> </xref> som inneholder alle statiske <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection"> </xref> objekter som er angitt i en <xref uid="langword_csharp_<asp:proxywebpartmanager>" name="<asp:proxywebpartmanager>" href=""> </xref> elementet.

trans-unit.source: Overrides the base property to prevent a value from being assigned.
trans-unit.target: Overstyrer egenskapen base for å hindre at en verdi ble tilordnet.

trans-unit.source: The Visible property overrides the base property to prevent the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager> control from ever being made visible.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen Visible overstyrer egenskapen basistabellen slik at den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>kontrollen skulle det gjøres synlige.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager> control, like the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control, has no user interface (UI) and is never displayed to the user.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>kontrollere, som den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontrollere, har ingen brukergrensesnittet (UI) og aldri vises for brukeren.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: Always returns <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>, to prevent the control from being made visible.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer alltid <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>, for å hindre at kontrollen gjøres synlige.

trans-unit.source: A caller tries to assign a value to this property.
trans-unit.target: En oppringer prøver å tilordne en verdi for denne egenskapen.
